{{Set(name="schema", value=_sendReportInitialCheckSchemaSkill())}}

{{#system~}}
Based on the agent's <LastReply> you have to understand if they promised to pass information to the manager right away. Agent must clearly state that they are going to pass information to the manager right now. So their <LastReply> should contain something like: "I will pass this information to the manager right away...", "I will pass all details to the manager right away...", etc. If the <LastReply> differs set field promised to false.

**Note:** The Agent can talk in different languages.

<LastReply>
{{agentAnswer}}
</LastReply>

{{~/system}}
{{Set(name="promise", value=Gen(jsonSchema=schema, validateSchema="True", temperature=0.2, topP=0, thinkingBudget=85))}}

{{#if GetValueJSON(obj=promise, key="promised") == "true"}}
    {{SendMessage(
        message="System log: Send report is executed during conversation.",
        actorIds=_utilsGetFootnoteSkill(userId=userId, system="True")
    )}}
    {{_sendReportSkill(transcript=transcript, userId=userId)}}
{{/if}}
